PRB02-PRB02-003 normal.name: Lucky.Roux
PRB02-PRB02-003 normal.description:
[Blocker] (After your opponent declares an attack, you may rest this card to make it the new target of the attack.)
[On Play] You may trash 1 Character card with 6000 power or more from your hand: Draw 2 cards.

PRB02-PRB02-004 normal.name: Jewelry Bonney
PRB02-PRB02-004 normal.description:
[Blocker] (After your opponent declares an attack, you may rest this card to make it the new target of the attack.)
[On Your Opponent's Attack] [Once Per Turn] Set up to 1 of your DON!! cards as active.

PRB02-PRB02-005 normal.name: Monkey.D.Luffy
PRB02-PRB02-005 normal.description: [Your Turn] [On Play] If your Leader is multicolored and your opponent has 7 or less DON!! cards on their field, your opponent rests 1 of their active DON!! cards at the start of their next Main Phase.

PRB02-PRB02-012 normal.name: Nami
PRB02-PRB02-012 normal.description:
[On Play] Look at 5 cards from the top of your deck; reveal up to 1 "Straw Hat Crew" type card other than [Nami] and add it to your hand. Then, place the rest at the bottom of your deck in any order.
[Trigger] Play this card.

PRB02-PRB02-009 normal.name: Mr.3(Galdino)
PRB02-PRB02-009 normal.description:
This effect can be activated when this Character is rested by your opponent's effect. You may trash this Character and draw 2 cards.
[Blocker]

PRB02-PRB02-016 normal.name: Otama
PRB02-PRB02-016 normal.description:
[Activate: Main] You may rest this Character and add 1 card from the top or bottom of your Life cards to your hand: Up to 1 of your Leader or Character cards gains +3000 power during this turn.
[Trigger] Rest up to 1 of your opponent's Characters with a cost of 4 or less.

PRB02-PRB02-015 normal.name: Shiryu
PRB02-PRB02-015 normal.description:
If your Leader has the "Blackbeard Pirates" type, this Character gains [Blocker] and +4 cost.
[On K.O.] If your Leader has the "Blackbeard Pirates" type, K.O. up to 1 of your opponent's Characters with a base cost of 4 or less.

PRB02-PRB02-002 parallel.name: Trafalgar Law - PRB02-002
PRB02-PRB02-002 parallel.types: Heart Pirates;The Seven Warlords of the Sea;Punk Hazard
PRB02-PRB02-002 parallel.description:
[Once Per Turn] If this Character would be removed from the field by your opponent's effect, you may give this Character -2000 power during this turn instead.
[When Attacking] Give up to 1 of your opponent's Characters -2000 power during this turn.

PRB02-PRB02-001 normal.name: Koby
PRB02-PRB02-001 normal.description:
[Opponent's Turn] If your Leader has the "Navy" type, this Character gains +1000 power.
[When Attacking] K.O. up to 1 of your opponent's Characters with 3000 base power or less. Then, if you have 6 or less cards in your hand, draw 1 card.

PRB02-PRB02-006 normal.name: Roronoa Zoro - PRB02-006
PRB02-PRB02-006 normal.description:
[Opponent's Turn] If this Character would be rested by your opponent's Character's effect, you may rest 1 of your other Characters instead.
[Blocker]

PRB02-PRB02-010 normal.name: Charlotte Pudding
PRB02-PRB02-010 normal.description: [On Play] DON!! -2: If your Leader has the "Big Mom Pirates" type and your opponent has 6 or more DON!! cards on their field, draw 2 cards. Then, play up to 1 "Big Mom Pirates" type Character card with 6000 to 8000 power from your hand.

PRB02-PRB02-011 normal.name: Donquixote Doflamingo
PRB02-PRB02-011 normal.types: Donquixote Pirates;The Seven Warlords of the Sea
PRB02-PRB02-011 normal.description:
[Blocker]
[On Play] If your Leader is multicolored, add up to 1 DON!! card from your DON!! deck and rest it.
